## 3. CANONICAL FORMATION

Canonical is set explicitly in frontmatter. The system also auto-derives it identically:

```
canonical: https://mirelleinspo.com/blog/{topic}/{slug}   ŌåÉ if topic exists
canonical: https://mirelleinspo.com/blog/{slug}            ŌåÉ if no topic
```

**Always set canonical explicitly in frontmatter** ŌĆö match the URL exactly. No trailing slash.

